WEBVTT

00:12.960 --> 00:15.080
This is 327, I'm going in.

00:15.500 --> 00:17.080
Good luck, agent.

00:43.440 --> 00:46.000
Hello! I was just admiring the...

00:54.840 --> 00:57.550
...art. Haircut, but...

00:57.560 --> 01:03.390
Please, such a lovely place you've got here.
Is it usually this...

01:25.200 --> 01:28.000
...empty? Just a trim, please.

02:41.840 --> 02:44.910
Chief, you copy? I need backup!

02:44.920 --> 02:51.630
What are you doing? No!

02:51.640 --> 02:58.590
It looks like we've found our next recruit.
Doctor, carry on with the procedure.

02:58.600 --> 03:05.890
We have to make room for Agent 327.
